# Environment Variables Example

# Currency Conversion API: exchangerate-api.com (Free Tier)
# =========================================================
# Endpoint: https://open.er-api.com/v6/latest/USD
# Features: Real-time exchange rates for 160+ currencies
# API Key: Not required for free tier (1,500 requests/month)
# Status: Fully CORS-enabled, excellent uptime
#
# No environment variables needed for the free tier!
# The app uses the public free endpoint directly.
#
# If you need higher limits (paid tier), set:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_EXCHANGE_RATE_API_URL=https://v6.exchangerate-api.com/v6/YOUR_API_KEY/latest/USD

# Note: Current setup only uses public endpoints with no authentication required
